channel.title: Need Help Finding An Error
channel.description:
I'm currently working on some new graphics for the lesser demons. Apart from the attack animation they're PERFECT, one problem though. When ever I see the graphics in-game I get a dived by zero error. I know that this is because one or more of the values I have inputted is wrong. I can't find it no matter what I try. Please download my graphics (spr files) and see if you can find what's wrong. It would help me and my mod out significantly, thank you :D
Here's the one of the files as proof that it's what your downloading :
[IMG]http://img188.imageshack.us/img188/5976/92369425.png[/img]
I didn't make these graphics btw, I'm just using them.
Download : http://www.mediafire.com/file/0noc1mkngwm/sprites.rar
